rows.label: qst702703_msg0001
rows.name:
I need you to defeat the monsters that
have set up camp in front of the bridge
to the Haradd Hills.

rows.label: qst702703_msg0002
rows.name:
If I don't make the delivery in time,
my father will fly off the handle...

rows.label: qst702703_msg0003
rows.name:
I hope you deal with it soon!
You're my only hope.

rows.label: qst702703_msg0101
rows.name:
Oh, you got rid of them?!
Drivers sure have some skills...
Thanks a bunch!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0102
rows.name:
"Simple manual labor," my arse...
Nothing simple about this, ya codger!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0103
rows.name:
...Ugh, and still, I've gotta hurry
if I don't want to get fed a
knuckle sandwich...

rows.label: qst702703_msg0104
rows.name:
Here! I've not got much to offer,
but take this, with my thanks.

rows.label: qst702703_msg0105
rows.name:
We work as gardeners in the capital,
my dad and me. If you're ever in the
area, come say hi!

rows.label: qst702703_msg0106
rows.name:
Right-o then...
How much sand did he say we
needed again...?

rows.label: qst702703_msg0107
rows.name:
Eh, I'll remember along the way,
I'm sure.
